title: Cal Smart 'Chalet'-Style Chicken Tenders with Carrots, Peas and Smashed Potatoes
description: This Cal Smart take on the rotisserie classic is packed with comforting savoury flavours! Seasoned salt coats juicy chicken and wholesome veggies, all covered in a rich gravy infused with chicken broth and our timeless gravy spice blend.

